750
01:38:01.399 --> 01:38:04.319
I know what you have to do.

751
01:38:06.488 --> 01:38:09.282
But let me do it.

752
01:38:17.499 --> 01:38:20.377
Let me do it.

753
01:38:42.691 --> 01:38:45.944
You look like someone else.

754
01:39:07.632 --> 01:39:09.551
Good night, Betty.

755
01:39:09.759 --> 01:39:12.512
You don't have to wear
that in the house.

756
01:39:12.888 --> 01:39:14.472
What?

757
01:39:14.681 --> 01:39:16.474
The wig!

758
01:39:16.725 --> 01:39:22.105
I was just looking at myself again.
I'll take it off to sleep.

759
01:39:22.772 --> 01:39:25.233
You don't have
to sleep on that couch.

760
01:39:25.442 --> 01:39:29.613
- No, it's okay.
- No, it's not. This is a huge bed.

761
01:39:29.946 --> 01:39:32.032
Come on, just get in
and get a good night sleep.

762
01:40:04.231 --> 01:40:07.567
It's more comfortable than
the couch, isn't it?

763
01:40:16.785 --> 01:40:18.954
Thank you, Betty.

764
01:40:19.663 --> 01:40:24.376
It's nothing. I shouldn't have let
you sleep on the couch last night.

765
01:40:24.584 --> 01:40:26.378
No, I mean...

766
01:40:27.212 --> 01:40:29.381
thank you for everything.

767
01:40:33.635 --> 01:40:35.262
You're welcome.

768
01:40:45.438 --> 01:40:47.899
Good night, sweet Betty.

769
01:40:57.534 --> 01:40:59.661
Good night.

770
01:41:41.494 --> 01:41:44.164
Have you ever done this before?

771
01:41:45.582 --> 01:41:47.667
I don't know.

772
01:41:47.876 --> 01:41:49.461
Have you?

773
01:42:03.600 --> 01:42:06.520
I want to with you.

774
01:42:32.087 --> 01:42:35.131
I'm in love with you.

775
01:42:49.104 --> 01:42:52.107
I'm in love with you.

